data.text: I’ll always be loving and kind I always see the best in ppl so to all my followers to my family friends and to the twitter followers who love me thank you ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️

Clearly the ppl who have sent me some nasty tweets are keyboard warriors with nothing better to do. I’m gunna keep being my loving kind self supporting the ppl that inspire me as for the ppl sending me hate tweets I’m not watsting any more of my energy on hateful tweets
